title: Android Auto connection issues in 2020 Subaru Outback
content: I just bought a 2020 Subaru Outback and tried to connect my Android Auto to my car. I was unable to since the software is only compatible with the 2018 Outback at the latest according to Subaru's website. Is there a fix for this or do I just have to be patient for an update? Thank you!
category: Connectivity, Network, Bluetooth, Google Pixel 3 XL
